\subsection softwareResources Online Resources

The CVS repository for Acro is on software.sandia.gov.  This machine supports a variety of tools to facilitate the development of software tools, including
<ol>

<li> Bugzilla (<a href="http://software.sandia.gov/bugzilla/">http://software.sandia.gov/bugzilla/</a>) - online bug reporting

<li> Mailman (<a href="http://software.sandia.gov/mailman/listinfo/">http://software.sandia.gov/mailman/listinfo/</a>) - mailing list management

<li> Bonsai (<a href="http://software.sandia.gov/bonsai/cvsqueryform.cgi">http://software.sandia.gov/bonsai/cvsqueryform.cgi</a>) - a query interface to CVS
</ol>

The following mailing lists are supported for Acro:
<ol>

<li><a href="http://software.sandia.gov/mailman/private/acro-announce/">acro-announce@software.sandia.gov</a> - general announcements

<li><a href="http://software.sandia.gov/mailman/private/acro-bugs/">acro-bugs@software.sandia.gov</a> - bug reports

<li><a href="http://software.sandia.gov/mailman/private/acro-checkins/">acro-checkins@software.sandia.gov</a> - CVS checking reports

<li><a href="http://software.sandia.gov/mailman/private/acro-developers/">acro-developers@software.sandia.gov</a> - a developers mailing list

<li><a href="http://software.sandia.gov/mailman/private/acro-help/">acro-help@software.sandia.gov</a> - a help list

<li><a href="http://software.sandia.gov/mailman/private/acro-misc-checkins/">acro-misc-checkins@software.sandia.gov</a> - CVS checking reports for miscellaneous acro components

<li><a href="http://software.sandia.gov/mailman/private/acro-users/">acro-users@software.sandia.gov</a> - a general users' mailing list

</ol>
The mailman server also includes some mailing lists for specific Acro components like APPSPACK, PICO and Coliny.
